Package ca.phon.plugin

Annotation Type PhonPlugin

  • @Target(TYPE)
@Retention(RUNTIME)
public @interface PhonPlugin
    Annotation for used for Phon plugins. This annotation must exist for any phon plug-in extension point.

    • Optional Element Summary
